title: Team's win-loss shows up correctly
custom_preconds:
GIVEN I an postseason brackets page
AND the Yankees have made it to the Postseason
custom_steps:
WHEN I look into the Yankees seed
AND I collect their win-loss record
AND I make an HTTP call to statsapi with the Yankees record: https://beta-statsapi.mlb.com/api/v1/teams/147?hydrate=standings(season=2024)
AND I store the win loss values in a variable
AND I make an HTTP call to graphQL with the proper query to https://data-graph-beta.mlb.com/graphql
AND I store the wins and losses from the response body as follows:
wins = data.bracket.rounds[0].matchups[0].topSeed.stats.record.leagueRecord.wins
losses = data.bracket.rounds[0].matchups[0].topSeed.stats.record.leagueRecord.losses
custom_expected: THEN I should see the wins and losses record match between stats-api & graphQL response & the UI
